  "text": "This concept describes a person's willingness to change and to innovate within a complex and ambiguous network of problems [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Consequently, innovation competence could be expressed in one's inclination to be challenged by unanswered questions, ambiguities and unresolved problems [CITATION_3] .",
